restart
online help

composting:
xcompmgr 
display settings:
zarfy 
https://sourceforge.net/projects/zarfy/
http://gungre.ch/dragora/repo/kelsoo/zarfy/source/
http://gungre.ch/dragora/repo/kelsoo/zarfy/zarfy-0.1.0-i486-1.tlz  #32bit

